the companys fiscal year is the 52 or 53-week periodthat ends on the last saturday of
september.the companys fiscal years 2014,2013 and 2012 ended on september27, 2014,september28, 2013 and september29, 2012, respectively.both fiscal years 2014 and 2013 spanned 52 weeks. fiscal year
2012spanned 53 weeks, with a 14th week included in the first quarter of 2012, as is done approximately every six years to realign the companys fiscal quarters more closely to calendar
quarters. inclusion of theadditional week in 2012 increasedthe companys overall net sales and operatingexpenses for the year.
